<div class="container">
    <h2>University Admission Registration Criteria</h2>
    <p>Please read the following criteria carefully before proceeding to the application form.</p>

    <h3>Eligibility Criteria:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Minimum age of 17 years</li>
        <li>High school diploma or equivalent</li>
        <li>Minimum GPA of 2.5 or equivalent</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Required Documents:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>High school transcript</li>
        <li>Birth certificate</li>
        <li>Passport-sized photograph</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Application Requirements:</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>Completed application form</li>
        <li>Application fee (non-refundable)</li>
        <li>English language proficiency test scores (if applicable)</li>
    </ul>

    <p>By proceeding to the application form, you confirm that you meet the eligibility criteria and have the required documents ready.</p>

    <button asp-action="ApplicationForm" asp-controller="Admissions" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">
        Proceed to Form
    </button>
</div>

